plot: The Emperor uses the information on the recovered Holocrons to launch devastating attacks on planets sympathetic to the Rebellion. Luke knows there's only one solution: a daring raid on Coruscant to get the Holocrons back.
title: The New Yoda Chronicles: Raid on Coruscant
